{"tid":1589973,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"屌，係屋企好難頂","createTime":"2019-09-23T13:35:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-23T13:43:18.000Z","uid":317712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"a5cbca461d4517e6c7be748addbfc1ec20e6053e","tid":1589973,"uid":317712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T13:35:48.000Z","msg":"事源我屋企就好撚藍<br />\n每次講講下我屋企人就一定會講到「啲人咪又係出黎搞事」「咪搞到咁亂啦」「舉美國旗有冇睇過美國人權第幾名」乜乜柒柒<br />\n<br />\n其實佢都係香港大，點解要講呢啲，成日用搵食做理由「人地搵食好辛苦，無錢唔得」<br />\n<br />\n差唔多講到呢到我通常都唔撚會再出聲，由佢講，<br />\n但只係聽都唔撚掂<br />\n<br />\n其實可以講啲咩一下收佢皮<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">Btw929,101記得出嚟</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"2400fae22b13df32628de9adfa910847349755df","tid":1589973,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T13:36:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YY8gJwH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYY8gJwH.jpg&h=de149ef0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n［行動］929細節出左了 唔該文宣 推爆佢 (2)<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1589858\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1589858</a>"},{"pid":"f7f0bb4362b1d3091ba86b456a969d5106473c5e","tid":1589973,"uid":146285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T13:43:18.000Z","msg":"你：我冇留意啲排名呀，你講解吓中國人權第幾名比我聽丫? <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}